flowRoot.flowPara: This file provides a predictable SVG input for idforge-qatest(1) command to validate production processes implemented by idforge-render(1) and idforge-locale(1) commands. This file is specially conceived to validate idforge(1) environments related to image rendition.

As result of processing the =CONFIG_SECTIONS= configuration sections, using the production standards implemented by idforge-render(1) command, you must see a composition with idFORGE brand on document's header, document's background and document's footer.
